title: The Gonzo Tapes: The Life and Work of Dr. Hunter S. Thompson
description:
The Gonzo Tapes: The Life and Work of Dr. Hunter S. Thompson
Release Date: October 28, 2008

All ripped at 192kbps. These were recorded on small machines, so that&#039;s probably more than needed to preserve the essence.

Program that I used for ripping didn&#039;t transfer the track titles. They are all rather long, so being lazy, I scanned the back of the jewel cases to serve as an index.
